## Suggestion discipline

1. Identify department first; never blend unrelated forms.
2. Pick one FMS from catalog or one custom FMS scoped to that department.
3. Each stage = one form; include catalog key fields + universal fields.
4. Suggest additions (SLA, proof, approvals, WhatsApp, KPIs, sheet columns) without removing core fields unless user opts out.

